The area herein declared for disposition is subject to final survey and shall be administered and disposed of by the National Housing Authority under the provisions of UDHA Law or R.A. 7279, particularly Sections 8 and 12 thereof, in coordination with AFP/DND.

The portion or portions of the area herein declared open for disposition that are being used or earmarked for public or quasi-public purposes shall be excluded from such disposition.

IN WITNESS WHEREOF , I have hereunto set my hand and caused the seal of the Republic of the Philippines to be affixed.

Done in the City of Manila, this 1st day of May in the year of Our Lord, two thousand and four.

(Sgd.) GLORIA MACAPAGAL-ARROYO

By the President: (Sgd.) ALBERTO G. ROMULO Executive Secretary

